commit.message:
Improved the handling of suboption arguments that look like options
(i.e. begin with one or two dashes and a letter).

Do NOT consider command line arguments starting with dash+space as an
option.

Add a variant of "FileTransformations.transfor(String[] args...)" that
treats file name "-" as STDIN or STDOUT.
Improved the handling of sub-options: These can now be terminated with "--"; unknown sub-options are now detected realiably (and not taken as following option arguments).
